    "attributes": {
        "action": "Impose a blanket ban on deep sea mining",
        "additional_details": "Deep sea mining has the potential to cause untold damage and potential destruction to pristine, undisturbed eco-systems.\r\n \r\nThe physical reality of drilling will lead to vast plumes of thick sediment being released over fragile and beautiful eco-systems while these same eco-systems would endure noise pollution which could affect sea animals\u2019 ability to communicate with each other.",
        "background": "Impose a blanket ban on all deep sea mining by the UK, to ensure our country has no part to play in exploiting our oceans.",
